eNCA reporter Nobesuthu Hejana is there and joins us live. #DStv403 CAPE TOWN - With crime on the rise, the Police Minister is hosting an Imbizo which some say is just another talk shop. On Monday five people were gunned down in Khayelitsha in Cape Town. This is by no means an isolated incident. On Thursday, Cape Town residents told Police Minister Bheki Cele how they regularly have to dodge bullets and fend off criminals.